My experience at the Starbucks located on Court Street and Joralemon Street, Brooklyn, NYC 11201 is the absolute best in show for their customer service. From the first point of contact crew, to the Baristas and to the manager, that I met, Mark (not sure if he is still there, but he left the best impression of leadership on my mind)! From July - December, I was on medical leave.  Upon my second day of return to work, I stopped by Starbucks and was welcomed by Cam, a mist gracious and impeccably appointed ambassador of Starbucks.  He took my order and as we chatted as we closed the transaction.  I asked about a colleague, whose name I could not recall. I learned that she is well and as I forgot her name again I am touched with joy to hear that she is well. The wait time was not enough for the pleasant team and their beautiful and award winning smiles! I am grateful for their collective teamwork and their kind and generous attitude as well as their commitment to their customers and the Starbucks company brand! Thank you so much... Traylor
